text:
29 Seconds of Farcaster ... What did you miss this (long) weekend?

* An era of $DEGEN has ended as allocations are finished and we move toward the mini app & client era. Thanks to @jacek for an amazing run and here's to the future of the hat! üé© 

* @betrmint released a $BETR staking rewards claim with daily spins of the NEON wheel to get your daily rewards & a shot at a jackpot for anyone with 10M $BETR staked. s/o @toadyhawk.eth & @netnose for the design & @burrrrrberry for keeping the FUN in staking claims ü•© daily available in the mini app

* $BRACKY stepped it up with Football--College & NFL and is headed to X/Twitter this Fall. There were some serious Bracky sessions Friday night after the football release

* @bertwurst.eth held a Labor Day 'Toy Draft' for the ceremonial exchanging of 'active' toys for September and live-streamed it. Bert seemed thrown off at first by the new format, but eventually 'Roadkill' was the winner and @erica & @laurenmessner had the top brackets and received face licks, tail wags, & generational wealth

* A bit more niche, but @mcbain shared some videos about his inspiring work trying to turn his neighborhood into a community--which may be useful for some, but also shows off why Farcasters are great. It even led to Presidential campaign rumors from a certain /gmfarcaster host.

* Speaking of /gmfarcaster @adrienne & @nounishprof are on today at 11:30 AM EST/ 8:30 PST to catch you up on all things purple (and blue)

show_title: Locking In September (But Halfway, Because Horses üêé): GM Farcaster ep284
text:
Why mini apps over websites? 

Mini Apps in Farcaster‚Äôs context is much more than accessing a crypto service with your wallet baked in

It‚Äôs also your connections, your history, your content, your entire context‚Äî what you prefer, how you interact, what tokens you hold, who do you respond to, publicly 

Mini Apps that build on Farcaster get to leverage their user‚Äôs entire context to make them highly personalized instantly (results in higher conversion)

I wrote about it a few days ago‚Äî Apps fit well because Farcaster acts as an operating system for the ecosystem 

https://farcaster.xyz/tanishq/0x972e8fee

cast.text:
My thesis for Farcaster as an operating system has only gotten stronger

> Decentralized social graph
> Mini Apps & App Coins
> Integrated wallet
> Embedded tokens in casts
> Token discovery
> Near-instant cross chain swaps
> and so many upcoming primitives

Developers can create permissionless apps (social graph, wallet) and incentivize people (tips) for distribution (embedded tokens in casts), tap into cross-chain liquidity with no trace of friction.

- @noiceapp sends a tip in $lemon3
- @tipn sends a tip in $USDC

(Not to mention tips in $DEGEN, recently $BETR, etc)
